### Create invoice for patient
POST http://localhost:8080/api/invoices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient": { "id": 1 },
  "issuedBy": { "id": 1 },
  "status": "PENDING"
}

### Get all invoices
GET http://localhost:8080/api/invoices
Accept: application/json

### Get invoice by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/invoices/1
Accept: application/json

### Add invoice item
POST http://localhost:8080/api/invoice-items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoice": { "id": 1 },
  "description": "Clinic visit",
  "quantity": 1,
  "unitPrice": 300.0
}

### Get all invoice items
GET http://localhost:8080/api/invoice-items
Accept: application/json

### Create payment for invoice
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoice": { "id": 1 },
  "amount": 300.0,
  "method": "CASH",
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### Get all payments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Accept: application/json
